红雀队宣布推出首张 EP 并分享令人沉思的新单曲“If I Could Make You Care” https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardinals-announce-debut-ep-and-share-brooding-new-single-if-i-could-make-you-care-3615050?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=红雀队宣布首次亮相并分享沉思新单曲如果我能让你关心Emma WilkesMon, 08 Apr 2024 21:07:49 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3615050 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/cardinals-press-image-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="红雀队" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/cardinals-press-image-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/cardinals-press-image-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/cardinals-press-image-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/cardinals-press-image-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/cardinals-press-image-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/cardinals-press-image-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “它的核心是流行音乐，个性化、年轻化，如果你能超越混乱和噪音，它会非常温暖。”主唱尤安·曼宁说道</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardinals-announce-debut-ep-and-share-brooding-new-single-if-i-could-make-you-care-3615050">红雀队宣布首张 EP 并分享令人沉思的新单曲“If I Could Make You Care”</a>后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/cardinals-press-image-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="红雀队" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/cardinals-press-image-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/cardinals-press-image-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/cardinals-press-image-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/cardinals-press-image-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/cardinals-press-image-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/cardinals-press-image-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cardinals">红雀队</a>宣布推出他们的首张同名 EP，并分享了一首新单曲“If I Could Make You Care”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/cardinals-cork-band-roseland-interview-radar-3586733">红雀队：科克独立乐队致力于谱写未来经典</a></strong></li></ul><p>EP 将于 6 月 7 日通过 So Young Records 发行，由六首曲目组成，包括新单曲以及之前发行的热门歌曲《Unreal》和《Roseland》。</p><p> “这首歌的歌词除了标题之外没什么可说的，它是从<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-sinatra">Frank Sinatra</a>的《I Could Make You Care》中偷来的，”主唱尤安·曼宁 (Euan Manning) 谈到这首单曲时说道。</p><p>他继续说道：“这是我和奥斯卡共同撰写的，我们默默地努力，直到它成为我们之间的特殊作品。与乐队的安排带来了戏剧性和规模，它的规模超出了我们的预期。写这首歌让我松了口气，就好像我们已经走到了人生的某个阶段。”</p><p>在 EP 中，他补充道：“这是我们在科克城生活和玩耍时创作的歌曲集。它的核心是流行音乐，个性化、年轻化，而且，如果你能超越混乱和噪音，它会非常温暖。只要你有心去寻找，总会有一个故事。这是我们的第一张 EP，我们期待着它能够被所有人听到。”</p><p>查看下面的歌曲和 EP 曲目列表： </p><p><iframe title="红雀队 - 如果我能让你关心（官方视频）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/8zzwm7pz43Y?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <strong>“Cardinals”的曲目列表是：</strong></p><p> <strong>1.“扭转”</strong><br /> <strong>2.“不真实”</strong><br /> <strong>3.《玫瑰园》</strong><br /> <strong>4.“安非他明”</strong><br /> <strong>5.《十九》</strong><br /> <strong>6.“如果我能让你关心”</strong></p><p>乐队在二月份<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/cardinals-cork-band-roseland-interview-radar-3586733">接受<em>NME</em></a>采访时，曼宁讨论了他们的家乡科克对他们的影响：“我总是发现，无论我身在何处，都会对我产生很大的影响，影响我的生活方式以及我的生活方式。”我感觉，”他说。 “科克可能比都柏林、纽约或伦敦小得多，但我认为它充满了特色。感觉非常真实。”</p><p>与此同时，Cardinals 是上个月因音乐节与美国陆军的关系而退出<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/sxsw">SXSW</a>官方演出的众多爱尔兰乐队之一。来自该国的所有乐队——Kneecap <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/kneecap-and-sprints-join-list-of-artists-boycotting-sxsw-2024-3599443">、</a> Sprints、Soda Blonde、Gavin James、Robert Grace、Mick Flannery、Chalk、Gurriers、Enola Gay <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newdad-cardinals-enola-gay-and-rachel-chinouriri-issue-statements-on-sxsw-2024-boycott-support-victims-of-war-3600184">和 NewDad——</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/all-irish-bands-booked-have-now-pulled-out-of-sxsw-2024-in-solidarity-3600628">决定不再演出，声援</a>巴勒斯坦。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardinals-announce-debut-ep-and-share-brooding-new-single-if-i-could-make-you-care-3615050">红雀队宣布首张 EP 并分享令人沉思的新单曲“If I Could Make You Care”</a>后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
